, sier Gjerde."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|magasin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "03be01d26e9b4af6871915f7e978b6ab713080b39ea16095a72ff052d0fabe0c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-07-01T18:28:47.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Fortsatt leter halvparten av de fast ansatte ved Britannia Hotel etter jobb. N\u00e5r hotellet \u00e5pner d\u00f8rene igjen, vil nye fjes ta imot gjestene."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/magasin/article12979491.ece/gmlnzw/ALTERNATES/w980-default/BritanniaUke12.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/038007e0d3c8b86006dd9a8c1e7631e4ae93eb7d.jpg?593a4dac"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["De siste dagene p\u00e5 Britannia -adressa.no", "Utsetter jobbleting", "Kjent fasade", "Inspirert av det britiske", "Investerer"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "038007e0d3c8b86006dd9a8c1e7631e4ae93eb7d"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "magasin"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kjent fasade", "hotell", "bygge", "jobb", "\u00e5pne d\u00f8rene", "fast ansatte"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["dronningens", "nav", "e.c. dahls", "hotell-trondheim", "thon", "britannia hotel"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["gunnar houen", "kirsten renaa", "bjarte gjerde", "odd reitan"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", "pluss/magasin"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/magasin/article12979491.ece/gmlnzw/ALTERNATES/w980-default/BritanniaUk